Demonstration of indexed_block derived datatype

The same as indexed except that all blocks has the same block length.

    int MPI_Type_create_indexed_block(
        int count,
        int blocklength,
        const int array_of_displacements[],
        MPI_Datatype oldtype,
        MPI_Datatype *newtype
    )

    int bl = 3; // no. of elements of oldtype in each block
    MPI_Type_create_indexed_block(count, bl, disparray, oldtype, &newtype);
